** Reporting bugs **

Bugs should be reported to GuardSarm
(https://documentation.guardsarmsiem.com). Please, make sure to include
the following information:

-Output of "GUARDSARM_HOME/bin/guardsarm-control info"
-Content of GUARDSARM_HOME/etc/<guardsarm configuration file>
-Content of GUARDSARM_HOME/logs/<guardsarm log file>
-Operating system name/version (uname -a if Unix)
-Any other relevant information.


If you prefer to contact us privately or want to report a
security issue, send an e-mail to GuardSarm (security@guardsarmsiem.com).
